{
  "texts": [
    "Does it intend to deceive?",
    "Can it, in any literal sense, be said to have goals or aims?",
    "If so, does it intend to deceive us about the content of its utterances, or merely have the goal to appear to be a competent speaker?",
    "Does it have beliefs-internal representational states which aim to track the truth?",
    "If so, do its utterances match those beliefs (in which case its false statements might be something like hallucinations) or are its utterances not matched to the beliefs-in which case they are likely to be either lies or bullshit?"
  ]
}